{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 53,
    "name": "سُورَةُ النَّجۡمِ",
    "englishName": "An-Najm",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Star",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 62,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4785,
        "text": "以没落时的星辰发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4786,
        "text": "你们的同伴[穆圣]既没有迷误，也没有犯错。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4787,
        "text": "他未凭私欲而言。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4788,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]只是他所奉到的启示。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4789,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]是[安拉通过]强有力者[吉布里勒天使]教授他的。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4790,
        "text": "[吉布里勒天使]是纯洁的，达到了近乎完美。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4791,
        "text": "他[吉布里勒天使]在地平线的最高处，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4792,
        "text": "然后，他下降并逐渐接近。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4793,
        "text": "他相距两弓之长，或更近。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4794,
        "text": "他[安拉]把他要启示的[通过吉布里勒天使]启示他的仆人[穆圣]。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4795,
        "text": "他[穆圣]的心没有否认自己所见的。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4796,
        "text": "难道你们要同他[穆圣]争论他[升霄]所见的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4797,
        "text": "他[穆圣]确已看见他[吉布里勒天使]第二次下降[指另一次，并非升霄那一次]，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4798,
        "text": "在无尽[无人能通过]的酸枣树旁，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4799,
        "text": "酸枣树旁有永居的乐园。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4800,
        "text": "当酸枣树遮盖了应遮盖之物时，",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4801,
        "text": "[那时穆圣]目未邪视，也未过分[看不该看的]。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4802,
        "text": "他[穆圣]确已看见他的主[安拉]的一些最大的迹象。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4803,
        "text": "你们想过吗？拉特和欧宰[注][阿位伯人曾崇拜过的两个偶像]，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4804,
        "text": "以及第三个——马那[阿位伯人曾崇拜过的另一个偶像]。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4805,
        "text": "难道男性归你们，而女性归他[安拉]吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4806,
        "text": "如果这样，这确是最不公平的分配。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4807,
        "text": "这些偶像只是你们和你们的祖先所取的名称而已，安拉并未对此降示任何证据。他们只顺从猜想和私欲，尽管正道确已从他们的主降临他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4808,
        "text": "难道人想要什么就有什么吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4809,
        "text": "后世和今世都是安拉的。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 460,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4810,
        "text": "天上有许多天使，他们的求情毫无益处，除非安拉允许他们为他所意欲者和喜悦者求情之后。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 526,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4811,
        "text": "不信仰后世者，他们的确以女性的名字称呼天使们。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4812,
        "text": "他们对此毫无知识，他们只顺从猜想，而猜想绝不能替代真理。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4813,
        "text": "凡背弃我的教诲[《古兰经》]而只追求今世生活者，你当避开他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4814,
        "text": "这是他们知识的最高限度。你的主的确最知道谁是迷失正道者，也最知道谁是遵行正道者。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4815,
        "text": "天地间的一切都是安拉的。[复活日]，他将依作恶者所做的罪恶还报作恶者[如在火狱里惩罚他们]，将依行善者所做的最好善功报酬行善者[如让他们在乐园里享乐]。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4816,
        "text": "凡远避大罪[见6:152－153]和奸淫[注]，只犯小罪者，你的主确是最宽容的。当他从大地创造你们[如阿丹圣人]时，当你们还是胎儿在你们的母腹中时，他是最知道你们的。所以，你们不要自称纯洁，他最知道谁是敬畏者。",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 461,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4817,
        "text": "你[穆圣]注意到那个背离[伊斯兰教]的人吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4818,
        "text": "他稍微施舍就吝啬[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4819,
        "text": "难道他知道未见之物，因而他能看见[真理和结局]吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4820,
        "text": "难道没人告诉过他穆萨的经典中所记载的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4821,
        "text": "以及遵行所有主命的伊布拉欣的经典中所记载的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4822,
        "text": "一个负罪者不负担别人的罪恶。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4823,
        "text": "每人都将获得自己所奋斗的报酬[种瓜得瓜，种豆得豆]。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4824,
        "text": "[复活日]他奋斗的结果将被看见，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4825,
        "text": "然后，他将获得最完全的报酬。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4826,
        "text": "你的主[安拉]确是[万物]最终的归宿。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4827,
        "text": "他[安拉]的确能使[他所意欲的]人笑，他的确能使[他所意欲的]人哭。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4828,
        "text": "他的确能使[他所意欲的]人死，他的确能使[他所意欲的]人生。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 527,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4829,
        "text": "—",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4830,
        "text": "他的确用射出的一滴精液创造了配偶——男性和女性。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4831,
        "text": "[复活日]他的确以再造为己任。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4832,
        "text": "他的确能使[他所意欲的]人富裕，他的确能使[他所意欲的]人满意。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4833,
        "text": "他的确是天狼星[阿位伯人曾崇拜过的星]的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4834,
        "text": "他[安拉]的确毁灭了以前的阿德人，",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4835,
        "text": "以及萨姆德人，一个也没有留下。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4836,
        "text": "以前，[他曾毁灭了]努哈的族人。他们确是最不义的，确是最叛逆的[他们不服从安拉及其使者努哈]。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4837,
        "text": "他曾毁灭了被颠覆的城市[如鲁特圣人奉命生活过的巴勒斯坦所多玛城]。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4838,
        "text": "那覆盖之物[如石雨的刑罚]覆盖了被颠覆的城市。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4839,
        "text": "[人啊！]你要怀疑你的主的哪项恩惠呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4840,
        "text": "这[穆圣]是以前那些警告者中的一位警告者。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4841,
        "text": "复活日临近了。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4842,
        "text": "除安拉外，绝没有人能解除它。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4843,
        "text": "难道你们对这训辞[《古兰经》]感到惊奇吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4844,
        "text": "你们怎么为此笑而不为此哭呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4845,
        "text": "你们[正在浪费宝贵的时间]消遣和娱乐[如唱歌跳舞]。",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4846,
        "text": "你们当向安拉叩头，当崇拜他。叩头处",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 462,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": {
          "id": 13,
          "recommended": false,
          "obligatory": true
        }
      }
    ],
